Date: Sat, 27 Dec 2025 20:34:51 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Update CMake minimum version to 3.10

Update CMake minimum required version from 3.0 to 3.10 to
suppress deprecation warnings when building with newer CMake.
---
 CMakeLists.txt | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/CMakeLists.txt b/CMakeLists.txt
index f5b3aa2..984a7f9 100644
--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
-cmake_minimum_required(VERSION 3.0)
+cmake_minimum_required(VERSION 3.10)
 project(rapidcheck CXX)
 
 # Don't warn about symbol visibility for static libraries with CMake 3.3 and later.
